Figure 5. OH-LAAO treatment did not affect body weight of mice. Changes in body weight of the mice in OH-LAAO-treated group and control group were de-
termined weekly. There was no significant differences in the average body weight of the two groups over the 8 weeks treatment period (P > 0.05). Solid line -■-: Treated mice; 
Broken line ---♦---: Control mice. Data was expressed as mean ± SEM.
